{
  "id": "adv_event_2107_01_02",
  "title": "雨上がりの太陽と共に第2話　ジンクス",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-chs001.wav",
      "text": "私はあの有名な水族館に行きたいな",
      "startTime": 3.6666666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu001.wav",
      "text": "せやな、沖縄観光するなら水族館はマストやねぇ",
      "startTime": 8.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk002.wav",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "startTime": 13.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-szk001.wav",
      "text": "観光と言えば世界遺産は外せない……",
      "startTime": 15.166666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "昔の城跡とかパワースポットな聖地とか",
      "startTime": 18.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu002.wav",
      "text": "沖縄は見所が沢山あるからなぁ",
      "startTime": 22.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk002.wav",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "startTime": 25.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私は沖縄の踊りを見てみたいわ",
      "startTime": 27.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-rei001.wav",
      "text": "手の動きに特徴があるのよね？",
      "startTime": 31.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "エイサーやカチャーシーやね",
      "startTime": 33.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu003.wav",
      "text": "一緒に踊るとめっちゃ盛り上がるんよ",
      "startTime": 36.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私はシーサーが見たいな～",
      "startTime": 38.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-skr001.wav",
      "text": "シーサーって可愛いよね～",
      "startTime": 41.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "シーサーはゆるキャラちゃうやん",
      "startTime": 44.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu004.wav",
      "text": "あと、さくらちゃんの可愛い基準おかしない？",
      "startTime": 47.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……ねえ、さっきから不思議に思ってたんだけど",
      "startTime": 50.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-rei002.wav",
      "text": "どうして優がいるの？",
      "startTime": 55.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今はサニピの沖縄旅行の話し合い……",
      "startTime": 57.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-szk002.wav",
      "text": "なのに自然に輪に入ってる……",
      "startTime": 60.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-chs002.wav",
      "text": "沖縄旅行じゃなくてお仕事だよ……",
      "startTime": 63.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まあまあえーやないの",
      "startTime": 66.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu005.wav",
      "text": "こう見えてもうちは沖縄について結構詳しいんよ",
      "startTime": 68.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk003.wav",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "startTime": 72.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……ところで、さっきから遙子さんはため息ばっかりで",
      "startTime": 74.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu006.wav",
      "text": "全然喋ってへんけど、どないしたん？",
      "startTime": 78.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-skr002.wav",
      "text": "遙子ちゃん、沖縄行きが決まってから元気がないんです",
      "startTime": 81.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-rei003.wav",
      "text": "理由を聞いても全然教えてくれないのよ",
      "startTime": 86.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-chs003.wav",
      "text": "あの……遙子さん、大丈夫？",
      "startTime": 89.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "え？　あ、ごめんなさい",
      "startTime": 93.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk004.wav",
      "text": "何でもないから気にしないで",
      "startTime": 95.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そない言われたら余計に気になるわ",
      "startTime": 98.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu007.wav",
      "text": "ずっと上の空で何考えてるん？",
      "startTime": 102.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk005.wav",
      "text": "それは……",
      "startTime": 105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みんな一緒の仲間やろ？",
      "startTime": 106.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu008.wav",
      "text": "悩みがあるなら、みんなで解決した方がええで？",
      "startTime": 109.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうよね。えっと……",
      "startTime": 113.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk006.wav",
      "text": "私は沖縄に行かない方がいいのかなって思って……",
      "startTime": 117.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-skr003.wav",
      "text": "えっ？　どういうこと？",
      "startTime": 123.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk007.wav",
      "text": "……実は私、沖縄と相性が悪いの",
      "startTime": 125.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "相性が悪い？",
      "startTime": 130.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu009.wav",
      "text": "沖縄に相性なんてあるん？",
      "startTime": 132.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "昔、ソロ時代の仕事で沖縄に行ったことがあるの",
      "startTime": 135.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk008.wav",
      "text": "その時は野外ステージで歌う予定だったんだけど……",
      "startTime": 140.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私が歌い始めたら突然スコールが降り出して",
      "startTime": 145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk009.wav",
      "text": "お客さんがみんないなくなっちゃったの",
      "startTime": 149.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私は土砂降りの雨に濡れながら",
      "startTime": 152.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk010.wav",
      "text": "誰もいない観客席に向かって歌ったわ……",
      "startTime": 155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
